{"tid":2363884,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"2010-2020西甲過人次數榜單：球王梅西居首，領先第二名1010次","createTime":"2021-01-12T14:14:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T15:32:48.000Z","uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eeaa7eea880f3bfd0b1b9bcaea32856cd54d5a90","tid":2363884,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T14:14:50.000Z","msg":"&nbsp;據外媒足球數據網站統計，在過去10年的西甲聯賽中，梅西一共完成1617次盤帶過人，排名榜單第一。<br />\n<br />\n 而排在第二名的是來自畢爾巴鄂競技的穆尼亞因，他共完成607次，比梅西少了1010次。<br />\n<br />\n 2010-2021過人榜單TOP5:<br />\n<br />\n 1、梅西（巴塞羅那）&nbsp;1617次<br />\n<br />\n 2、穆尼亞因（畢爾巴鄂競技）&nbsp;607次<br />\n<br />\n 3、伊斯科（前馬拉加/皇家馬德里）&nbsp;527次<br />\n<br />\n 4、內馬爾（前巴塞羅那）&nbsp;493次<br />\n<br />\n 5、巴內加（前塞維利亞/前瓦倫西亞/前馬競）&nbsp;465次"},{"pid":"1ec5eb882cb11f384c88541700574c945584e972","tid":2363884,"uid":287385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T14:24:41.000Z","msg":"穆尼亞因.........."},{"pid":"072f981fb7983f824a1f5291154dc41a5756176d","tid":2363884,"uid":1734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T14:46:59.000Z","msg":"你一係轉撚返繁體字先post啦屌你老母 當呢到大陸？"},{"pid":"8bf318a1dc3fe45cb74625e26392a9919c2026ee","tid":2363884,"uid":1734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"072f981fb7983f824a1f5291154dc41a5756176d","tid":2363884,"uid":1734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T14:46:59.000Z","msg":"你一係轉撚返繁體字先post啦屌你老母 當呢到大陸？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T14:47:27.000Z","msg":"講錯係香港釋名"},{"pid":"2cba88dbb74747d3cc819102ec37bb807957f410","tid":2363884,"uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bf318a1dc3fe45cb74625e26392a9919c2026ee","tid":2363884,"uid":1734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"072f981fb7983f824a1f5291154dc41a5756176d","tid":2363884,"uid":1734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T14:46:59.000Z","msg":"你一係轉撚返繁體字先post啦屌你老母 當呢到大陸？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T14:47:27.000Z","msg":"講錯係香港釋名"},"citedBy